82
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:40,906
that is barreling down the road.

83
00:04:42,449 --> 00:04:45,035
And I'm looking at the truck.
And as soon as the light changes,

84
00:04:45,118 --> 00:04:47,037
the guy next to me,
